      • shimmerMenu1Listener

        OnItemClickListener shimmerMenu1Listener
        OnItemClickListener for the menu that is present in this activity. It holds a switch statement which reacts accordingly to whichever menu option was chosen. shimmermenu1 is the name of the menu that this OnItemClickListener is tied too.

        protected void onActivityResult(int requestCode,
                    int resultCode,
                    Intent data)
        This next function gets called automatically when the dialog windows that correspond to each menu choice are closed and the view returns to this activity
        Parameters:
        requestCode - the requestCode that was sent to the dialog window
        resultCode - either success or failure code, lets us know if the action failed or succeeded
        data - the intent that gets passed back from the dialog window
